<h5 id="subject_1039171">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=115560.msg1039171#msg1039171" rel="nofollow">Re: 【金字塔3-38】巴比伦崛起</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_1039171'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_1039171'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #4 于:</strong> 2020-03-08, 周日 21:37:33 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_1039171_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
